Ecology. Offshore rocky and coral reefs, well-known cleaner of coral and rocky reef fishes, typical depth range: 5–40 m (
Holthuis et al. 1980
;
Kassuga et al. 2015
).

Lysmata grabhami
is one of the most expensive ornamental shrimps marketed in the Brazilian aquarium trade and was included in the list of invertebrates exported from Brazil (Global Marine Ornamental Aquarium Database, GMAD;
Gasparini et al. 2005
).
